snippet.title: 5 FAVORITE FRAGRANCE NOTES (Mint, Amber, Oakmoss...) Pt. 2
snippet.description:

This is technically part 2 in this series, and in this episode I will share four fragrance recommendations for each the following key perfume ingredients: oakmoss, amber, mint, fig, and incense!
